column5: Hey all,  I noticed that there are a lot more guys on the board here from the Kitchener Waterloo area. I'm just wondering who would be interested in a get together?  Let me know if there's anyone interested?   Dave
I'd be up for meeting some locals!  Andrew.
I am in Kitchener myself, I`d be interested.
Sure.
Y'all gunna hold it at Bernie's in London? It's on Adelaide just south of Oxford. Can't miss it.
London is an hour away from Kitchener Roy. I'd hope we could find somewhere closer.
We could do something like Kelsey's on Fairway...Filthy McNasty's on Erb....Huether....something local
Sounds good - depending on the date, I'm up for that!
I'd be in for K or W...  let me know when and where. Filthy's or the 'Hooter' sound good
i'm in school this term (u of waterloo) so i'll be  in the area ... depending on time/date i might be able to show up
I'm in!
I'm in let me know a date and time.
When would be a good time for everyone? weekend? weekday?
Best day for me is Wednesday.  But other weekdays could work as well.
Any day after 6!
Dang! I feel that a poll is just around the corner.....
I figured they'd meet in a doughnut shop...around 3 am...
For coffee right????? I don't do donuts
I say we make a poll with days, times and places
Location doesn't really matter.. Huether is as good a place as any I guess.. weekday evenings are best...  Andrew.
I'd be game, depending on how my schedule fits.
Ahh the days when wednesday night at the heuther meant midweek strip club. have fun, i miss lion lager
